# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# PCMT AI Exam System — Production Environment
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# FRONTEND (Vercel) — Set these in Vercel Dashboard:
#   Project → Settings → Environment Variables
#
# BACKEND  (Render) — Set these in Render Dashboard:
#   Service → Environment
#
# This file is committed for Vercel build-time env vars (VITE_ prefix only).
# Backend secrets are NEVER committed — set them in Render Dashboard.
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── FRONTEND ONLY (Vercel build-time, VITE_ prefix required) ─────
# Point frontend to Render backend URL
VITE_API_URL=https://pcmt-ai-exam-backend.onrender.com
VITE_WS_URL=wss://pcmt-ai-exam-backend.onrender.com
